==== Summary

Agile continious testing.

In fact, it's more like /continious .*/, though it was designed primarily with
testing in mind.

==== Features

o test framework agnostic (test/unit, rspec, minitest, expectations, ...)
o web  framework agnostic (rails, merb, sinatra, camping, invisible, ...)
o Low level / Highly flexible
o Rediculously simple to use
o Simple code

